{"tid":2205663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門新路命名 區議員通過叫「浩光街」及「浩榮街」","createTime":"2020-09-17T03:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T01:51:29.000Z","uid":22556,"like":412,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee259f2ef1a80bc551fe90b542f82ed6339099e","tid":2205663,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:37:44.000Z","msg":"屯門至赤鱲角連接路預計10月開通，地政總署提議將道路正式命名為「屯門赤鱲角隧道公路」，並將兩條連接隧道的街道則建議分別命名為「浩和街」及「浩逸街」。屯門區議會財務、行政及宣傳委員會今早討論三段道路的命名，有民主派區議員反建議改名為「光復街」及「時代街」，最後區議會通過建議道路命名為「屯赤隧道公路」、「浩光街」及「浩榮街」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077434?fbclid=IwAR2AEZIdNuLKNgwtNZHGn1tn9Hyr_eUBoN8dEHWOHOcfoehPdeHKV4ZQpec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077434%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2AEZIdNuLKNgwtNZHGn1tn9Hyr_eUBoN8dEHWOHOcfoehPdeHKV4ZQpec&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=776b71b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1077434%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2AEZIdNuLKNgwtNZHGn1tn9Hyr_eUBoN8dEHWOHOcfoehPdeHKV4ZQpec&h=cd26c369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1077434?fbclid=IwAR2AEZIdNuLKNgwtNZHGn1tn9Hyr_eUBoN8dEHWOHOcfoehPdeHKV4ZQpec</a>"},{"pid":"1d319784fb63eeb3b634f3a0e2fb63b44ed70ea3","tid":2205663,"uid":6030,"like":8,"dislike":10,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:38:34.000Z","msg":"浩男街"},{"pid":"86d6cf45c36f42f8c03f28303413d5fa0beb73fb","tid":2205663,"uid":284699,"like":57,"dislike":4,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"溝埋做瀨尿牛丸......."},{"pid":"5c47fb179095d43c885559b35c4f26d206289383","tid":2205663,"uid":46459,"like":82,"dislike":2,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T03:40:59.000Z","msg":"赤豕公路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e022bc881bd7108dacf83797633bf5abe620c2","tid":2205663,"uid":196924,"like":293,"dislike":3,"score":290,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"赤龍幾撚型 點解唔